#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.2:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Mettāvagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 2. Paññāsutta → ādibrahmacariyapaññāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Paññāsutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, hetū aṭṭha paccayā ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:1.2"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satthāraṃ upanissāya viharati aññataraṃ vā "
"garuṭṭhāniyaṃ sabrahmacāriṃ, yatthassa tibbaṃ hirottappaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ "
"hoti pemañca gāravo ca."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo hetu paṭhamo paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.152"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:2.1"
msgid ""
"So taṃ satthāraṃ upanissāya viharanto aññataraṃ vā garuṭṭhāniyaṃ "
"sabrahmacāriṃ, yatthassa tibbaṃ hirottappaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti pemañca "
"gāravo ca, te kālena kālaṃ upasaṅkamitvā paripucchati paripañhati:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:2.2"
msgid "‘idaṃ, bhante, kathaṃ; imassa ko attho’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:2.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa te āyasmanto avivaṭañceva vivaranti, anuttānīkatañca uttānīkaronti, "
"anekavihitesu ca kaṅkhāṭhāniyesu dhammesu kaṅkhaṃ paṭivinodenti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:2.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo hetu dutiyo paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:3.1"
msgid ""
"So taṃ dhammaṃ sutvā dvayena vūpakāsena sampādeti—kāyavūpakāsena ca "
"cittavūpakāsena ca."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:3.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo hetu tatiyo paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:4.1"
msgid ""
"Sīlavā hoti, pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati ācāragocarasampanno "
"aṇumattesu vajjesu bhayadassāvī, samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:4.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho hetu catuttho paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
#. VAR: sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ → satthā sabyañjanā (si) | sātthaṃ savyañjanaṃ (pts1)
#. VAR: dhātā → dhatā (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an8.2:5.1"
msgid ""
"Bahussuto hoti sutadharo sutasannicayo. Ye te dhammā ādikalyāṇā "
"majjhekalyāṇā pariyosānakalyāṇā sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ "
"parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ abhivadanti, tathārūpāssa dhammā bahussutā honti "
"dhātā vacasā paricitā manasānupekkhitā diṭṭhiyā suppaṭividdhā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:5.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamo hetu pañcamo paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.153"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:6.1"
msgid ""
"Āraddhavīriyo viharati akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya, kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"upasampadāya, thāmavā daḷhaparakkamo anikkhittadhuro kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:6.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, chaṭṭho hetu chaṭṭho paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:7.1"
msgid "Saṅghagato kho pana anānākathiko hoti atiracchānakathiko."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:7.2"
msgid ""
"Sāmaṃ vā dhammaṃ bhāsati paraṃ vā ajjhesati ariyaṃ vā tuṇhībhāvaṃ "
"nātimaññati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:7.3"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, sattamo hetu sattamo paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:8.1"
msgid "Pañcasu kho pana upādānakkhandhesu udayabbayānupassī viharati:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:8.2"
msgid "‘iti rūpaṃ, iti rūpassa samudayo, iti rūpassa atthaṅgamo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:8.3"
msgid "iti vedanā, iti vedanāya samudayo, iti vedanāya atthaṅgamo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:8.4"
msgid "iti saññā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:8.5"
msgid "iti saṅkhārā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:8.6"
msgid "iti viññāṇaṃ, iti viññāṇassa samudayo, iti viññāṇassa atthaṅgamo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:8.7"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, aṭṭhamo hetu aṭṭhamo paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:9.1"
msgid "Tamenaṃ sabrahmacārī evaṃ sambhāventi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:9.2"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ kho āyasmā satthāraṃ upanissāya viharati aññataraṃ vā garuṭṭhāniyaṃ "
"sabrahmacāriṃ, yatthassa tibbaṃ hirottappaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti pemañca "
"gāravo ca."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:9.3"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: piyattāya garuttāya → piyatāya garutāya (s1-3)
msgctxt "an8.2:9.4"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(1)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.154"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:10.1"
msgid ""
"‘Taṃ kho panāyamāyasmā satthāraṃ upanissāya viharanto aññataraṃ vā "
"garuṭṭhāniyaṃ sabrahmacāriṃ, yatthassa tibbaṃ hirottappaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ "
"hoti pemañca gāravo ca, te kālena kālaṃ upasaṅkamitvā paripucchati "
"paripañhati:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:10.2"
msgid "“idaṃ, bhante, kathaṃ; imassa ko attho”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:10.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa te āyasmanto avivaṭañceva vivaranti, anuttānīkatañca uttānīkaronti, "
"anekavihitesu ca kaṅkhāṭhāniyesu dhammesu kaṅkhaṃ paṭivinodenti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:10.4"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:10.5"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(2)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:11.1"
msgid ""
"‘Taṃ kho panāyamāyasmā dhammaṃ sutvā dvayena vūpakāsena sampādeti—"
"kāyavūpakāsena ca cittavūpakāsena ca."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:11.2"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:11.3"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:12.1"
msgid ""
"‘Sīlavā kho panāyamāyasmā pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati "
"ācāragocarasampanno aṇumattesu vajjesu bhayadassāvī, samādāya sikkhati "
"sikkhāpadesu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:12.2"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:12.3"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(4)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:13.1"
msgid ""
"‘Bahussuto kho panāyamāyasmā sutadharo sutasannicayo. Ye te dhammā "
"ādikalyāṇā majjhekalyāṇā pariyosānakalyāṇā sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ "
"kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ abhivadanti, tathārūpāssa dhammā "
"bahussutā honti dhātā vacasā paricitā manasānupekkhitā diṭṭhiyā "
"suppaṭividdhā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:13.2"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:13.3"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(5)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:14.1"
msgid ""
"‘Āraddhavīriyo kho panāyamāyasmā viharati akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya, "
"kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ upasampadāya, thāmavā daḷhaparakkamo anikkhittadhuro "
"kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:14.2"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:14.3"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(6)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.155"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:15.1"
msgid "‘Saṅghagato kho panāyamāyasmā anānākathiko hoti atiracchānakathiko."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:15.2"
msgid ""
"Sāmaṃ vā dhammaṃ bhāsati paraṃ vā ajjhesati ariyaṃ vā tuṇhībhāvaṃ "
"nātimaññati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:15.3"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:15.4"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(7)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:16.1"
msgid ""
"‘Pañcasu kho panāyamāyasmā upādānakkhandhesu udayabbayānupassī viharati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:16.2"
msgid "iti rūpaṃ, iti rūpassa samudayo, iti rūpassa atthaṅgamo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:16.3"
msgid "iti vedanā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:16.4"
msgid "iti saññā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:16.5"
msgid "iti saṅkhārā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:16.6"
msgid "iti viññāṇaṃ, iti viññāṇassa samudayo, iti viññāṇassa atthaṅgamoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:16.7"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:16.8"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(8)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:17.1"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha hetū aṭṭha paccayā ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.2:17.2"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
